{"title":"Review: All-new Specialized Trail-Series Pant and Air Long Sleeve Jersey","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/03/03/review-all-new-specialized-trail-series-pant-and-long-sleeve-jersey/","date":1614779879000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p>Specialized recently announced their <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2021/02/16/specialized-spring-21-kit-for-road-trail-and-lifestyle-gets-plethora-technical-threads/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Spring ’21</a> collection of technical and casual apparel for road cyclists and mountain bikers. Details on most of the collection is thin on the ground but we do have the low-down on the all-new MTB Pants! We got the Specialized Trail-Series Pant and Air Long Sleeve Jersey in for testing. Here’s how we got on.</p><p><em>Images credit: Finlay Anderson</em></p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-SS21-trail-clothing-pants-jersey-review-fanderson-001.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-SS21-trail-clothing-pants-jersey-review-fanderson-001.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:484x323/rscb8/ng:webp/ngcb8\" alt=\"Specialized-Trail-Series Pant review ss21 collection\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-SS21-trail-clothing-pants-jersey-review-fanderson-001.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:484x323/rscb8/ng:webp/ngcb8\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-SS21-trail-clothing-pants-jersey-review-fanderson-001.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-SS21-trail-clothing-pants-jersey-review-fanderson-001-297x198.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-SS21-trail-clothing-pants-jersey-review-fanderson-001-800x533.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-SS21-trail-clothing-pants-jersey-review-fanderson-001-120x80.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-SS21-trail-clothing-pants-jersey-review-fanderson-001-768x512.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-SS21-trail-clothing-pants-jersey-review-fanderson-001-696x464.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-SS21-trail-clothing-pants-jersey-review-fanderson-001-1068x712.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-SS21-trail-clothing-pants-jersey-review-fanderson-001-630x420.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 630w\" ezoid=\"0.5046348944628356\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-SS21-trail-clothing-pants-jersey-review-fanderson-001.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-SS21-trail-clothing-pants-jersey-review-fanderson-001-297x198.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-SS21-trail-clothing-pants-jersey-review-fanderson-001-800x533.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-SS21-trail-clothing-pants-jersey-review-fanderson-001-120x80.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-SS21-trail-clothing-pants-jersey-review-fanderson-001-768x512.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-SS21-trail-clothing-pants-jersey-review-fanderson-001-696x464.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-SS21-trail-clothing-pants-jersey-review-fanderson-001-1068x712.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-SS21-trail-clothing-pants-jersey-review-fanderson-001-630x420.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 630w\"></a>Specialized have added the Trail-Series Pant to their Spring ’21 collection of technical apparel. Though listed in the Specialized Catalog under the Men’s section, we can confirm their somewhat unisex fit. These are not high waisted, designed instead to be worn on the rider’s hips where they are comfortable and secure.</p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-trail-series-pants-mtb-trouser-review-SS21-trail-clothing-fanderson-015.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-trail-series-pants-mtb-trouser-review-SS21-trail-clothing-fanderson-015.jpg\" alt=\"specialized trail series mtb trouser review pants ratchet buckle fastener\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-trail-series-pants-mtb-trouser-review-SS21-trail-clothing-fanderson-015.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-trail-series-pants-mtb-trouser-review-SS21-trail-clothing-fanderson-015.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-trail-series-pants-mtb-trouser-review-SS21-trail-clothing-fanderson-015-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-trail-series-pants-mtb-trouser-review-SS21-trail-clothing-fanderson-015-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-trail-series-pants-mtb-trouser-review-SS21-trail-clothing-fanderson-015-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-trail-series-pants-mtb-trouser-review-SS21-trail-clothing-fanderson-015-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-trail-series-pants-mtb-trouser-review-SS21-trail-clothing-fanderson-015-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-trail-series-pants-mtb-trouser-review-SS21-trail-clothing-fanderson-015-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-trail-series-pants-mtb-trouser-review-SS21-trail-clothing-fanderson-015-630x420.jpg 630w\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-trail-series-pants-mtb-trouser-review-SS21-trail-clothing-fanderson-015.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-trail-series-pants-mtb-trouser-review-SS21-trail-clothing-fanderson-015-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-trail-series-pants-mtb-trouser-review-SS21-trail-clothing-fanderson-015-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-trail-series-pants-mtb-trouser-review-SS21-trail-clothing-fanderson-015-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-trail-series-pants-mtb-trouser-review-SS21-trail-clothing-fanderson-015-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-trail-series-pants-mtb-trouser-review-SS21-trail-clothing-fanderson-015-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-trail-series-pants-mtb-trouser-review-SS21-trail-clothing-fanderson-015-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-trail-series-pants-mtb-trouser-review-SS21-trail-clothing-fanderson-015-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a></p><p>The main fabric of the Trail-Series Pants is composed of nylon (90%) and elastane (10%), with other areas containing a mix of nylon and spandex. The waist is not elasticated; fit is taken care of by a zip and a ratchet-style waist buckle. This is a durable choice of fastener, better than elastic that might lose its elasticity over time. It is also likely to weather the elements better than velcro, which tends to lose its grip in very wet, muddy conditions.</p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-Trail-Series-Pant-review-ss21-collection-fanderson-004.jpg\"><img loading=\"eager\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-Trail-Series-Pant-review-ss21-collection-fanderson-004.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng%3Awebp%2Fngcb8%2Frs%3Adevice%2Frscb8-1\" alt=\"Specialized-Trail-Series Pant review ss21 collection\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-Trail-Series-Pant-review-ss21-collection-fanderson-004.jpg 1200w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-Trail-Series-Pant-review-ss21-collection-fanderson-004-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-Trail-Series-Pant-review-ss21-collection-fanderson-004-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-Trail-Series-Pant-review-ss21-collection-fanderson-004-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-Trail-Series-Pant-review-ss21-collection-fanderson-004-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-Trail-Series-Pant-review-ss21-collection-fanderson-004-696x464.jpg 696w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-Trail-Series-Pant-review-ss21-collection-fanderson-004-1068x712.jpg 1068w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-Trail-Series-Pant-review-ss21-collection-fanderson-004-630x420.jpg 630w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\"></a></p><p>One of the most important features for any mountain bike pant is its ability to accommodate proper protective knee pads. A baggier area at the knees left plenty of room for our <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2020/11/30/review-bluegrass-solid-d3o-knee-pads-elbow-pads-are-functional-wearable-protection/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Bluegrass SOLID D30</a> knee pads. These pads are pretty well-endowed in their padding, with a big main pad made of D30 and additional padding at the outside and inside of the knee. The 4-way stretch fabric in this area permits ample freedom of movement for pedaling, even with the knee pads on.</p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-Trail-Series-Pant-review-SS21-trail-clothing-fanderson-006.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-Trail-Series-Pant-review-SS21-trail-clothing-fanderson-006.jpg\" alt=\"specialized trail series pant unisex fit tapered ankle cuff 4-way stretch fabric\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-Trail-Series-Pant-review-SS21-trail-clothing-fanderson-006.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-Trail-Series-Pant-review-SS21-trail-clothing-fanderson-006.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-Trail-Series-Pant-review-SS21-trail-clothing-fanderson-006-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-Trail-Series-Pant-review-SS21-trail-clothing-fanderson-006-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-Trail-Series-Pant-review-SS21-trail-clothing-fanderson-006-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-Trail-Series-Pant-review-SS21-trail-clothing-fanderson-006-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-Trail-Series-Pant-review-SS21-trail-clothing-fanderson-006-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-Trail-Series-Pant-review-SS21-trail-clothing-fanderson-006-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-Trail-Series-Pant-review-SS21-trail-clothing-fanderson-006-630x420.jpg 630w\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-Trail-Series-Pant-review-SS21-trail-clothing-fanderson-006.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-Trail-Series-Pant-review-SS21-trail-clothing-fanderson-006-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-Trail-Series-Pant-review-SS21-trail-clothing-fanderson-006-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-Trail-Series-Pant-review-SS21-trail-clothing-fanderson-006-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-Trail-Series-Pant-review-SS21-trail-clothing-fanderson-006-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-Trail-Series-Pant-review-SS21-trail-clothing-fanderson-006-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-Trail-Series-Pant-review-SS21-trail-clothing-fanderson-006-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-Trail-Series-Pant-review-SS21-trail-clothing-fanderson-006-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a></p><p>While baggy at the knee area, the Trail-Series Pant tapers off down to the ankle area, where an elasticated cuff hugs the ankle firmly. This tapering should help prevent the leg material from getting caught on the chain or anything you may have strapped to your down tube such as pump, tube/tire levers, etc.&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-mountain-bike-trousers-review-fanderson-011.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-mountain-bike-trousers-review-fanderson-011.jpg\" alt=\"specialized mtb pants review trail-series spring 21 collection\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-mountain-bike-trousers-review-fanderson-011.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-mountain-bike-trousers-review-fanderson-011.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-mountain-bike-trousers-review-fanderson-011-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-mountain-bike-trousers-review-fanderson-011-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-mountain-bike-trousers-review-fanderson-011-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-mountain-bike-trousers-review-fanderson-011-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-mountain-bike-trousers-review-fanderson-011-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-mountain-bike-trousers-review-fanderson-011-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-mountain-bike-trousers-review-fanderson-011-630x420.jpg 630w\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-mountain-bike-trousers-review-fanderson-011.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-mountain-bike-trousers-review-fanderson-011-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-mountain-bike-trousers-review-fanderson-011-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-mountain-bike-trousers-review-fanderson-011-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-mountain-bike-trousers-review-fanderson-011-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-mountain-bike-trousers-review-fanderson-011-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-mountain-bike-trousers-review-fanderson-011-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-mountain-bike-trousers-review-fanderson-011-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a></p><p>These MTB Pants aren’t waterproof, nor do they claim to be. They are however water repellent, and will keep your legs dry in very light drizzle or from the occasional splash through small puddles. The fabric is thicker than what we’ve seen on other mountain bike trousers, such as the Giro Havoc pants, and just feels to be of a higher quality. Laser cut holes on the inside leg add a little ventilation.</p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-mtb-pants-zippered-pockets-SS21-trail-clothing-fanderson-010.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ez