-fanderson-007-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-branding-arm-long-sleeve-jersey-mtb-apparel-review-spring-2021-SS21-trail-clothing-fanderson-007-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-branding-arm-long-sleeve-jersey-mtb-apparel-review-spring-2021-SS21-trail-clothing-fanderson-007-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a></p><p>While branding on the Trail-Series Pants is almost non-existent, it is fairly loud and proud on the women’s long sleeve jersey. That said, I actually quite like it. I think it’s kinda classy but it certainly won’t be everyone’s cup of tea. Paired with the color-matched MTB Pants, the jersey does have something of a factory look about it.</p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-SS21-trail-clothing-pants-jersey-review-fanderson-001.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-SS21-trail-clothing-pants-jersey-review-fanderson-001.jpg\" alt=\"Specialized-Trail-Series Pant review ss21 collection\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-SS21-trail-clothing-pants-jersey-review-fanderson-001.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-SS21-trail-clothing-pants-jersey-review-fanderson-001.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-SS21-trail-clothing-pants-jersey-review-fanderson-001-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-SS21-trail-clothing-pants-jersey-review-fanderson-001-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-SS21-trail-clothing-pants-jersey-review-fanderson-001-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-SS21-trail-clothing-pants-jersey-review-fanderson-001-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-SS21-trail-clothing-pants-jersey-review-fanderson-001-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-SS21-trail-clothing-pants-jersey-review-fanderson-001-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-SS21-trail-clothing-pants-jersey-review-fanderson-001-630x420.jpg 630w\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-SS21-trail-clothing-pants-jersey-review-fanderson-001.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-SS21-trail-clothing-pants-jersey-review-fanderson-001-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-SS21-trail-clothing-pants-jersey-review-fanderson-001-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-SS21-trail-clothing-pants-jersey-review-fanderson-001-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-SS21-trail-clothing-pants-jersey-review-fanderson-001-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-SS21-trail-clothing-pants-jersey-review-fanderson-001-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-SS21-trail-clothing-pants-jersey-review-fanderson-001-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Specialized-SS21-trail-clothing-pants-jersey-review-fanderson-001-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a></p><p>The fit is close but not tight. There’s room enough in the arms for low profile elbow pads like those from G-Form but I did struggle to get the Bluegrass SOLID D30 elbow pads under there comfortably. The fabric is soft, thin and lightweight to the touch, and wicks sweat away nicely. This is an appropriate mid-layer for frosty morning rides in spring.</p><h3>Pricing &amp; Availability</h3><p>The Specialized-Trail-Series Pants are a unisex fit, available in sizes 24-44. There is also a Youth version on the way in sizes S, M &amp; L. It will get most of the features seen on the adult versions, but will only get one seam-sealed zippered leg pocket. Get them in Black or Cast Umber (shown here) for $135.</p><p>The Trail-Series Air long sleeve jersey is available in men’s and women’s cuts, in sizes XS-XXL. Get the women’s in Black or Cast Umber (women’s shown here) and the men’s in Black or Cast Battleship (navy) for $65.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.specialized.com/gb/en\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em>Specialized.com</em></a></p></div></div>","author":"Jessie-May Morgan","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"ad088336f52fc318714586b5deb1fec926c46d9d5c318d3ea3e90f8ee5016c2b","category":"Cycling"}